Popular actress, Tayo Sobola, better known as Sotayo Gaga has argued money is the main cause of stress in Nigeria. The movie star was conferred with the chieftaincy title of Sarauniya (Queen Mother) of Uke Kingdom Nasarawa State in December 2021. Taking to her Snap chat, she wrote: “Number 1 cause of stress is money.” Her assertion was seconded by most social media users mrpresidennnt said: “The language she spoke is called facts.” _aniscooser wrote: “Sometimes a credit alert can cure depressi0n… Money makes things better.” thegirltessy stated: “If I get money like this all my stress don go.” Read Also: Sotayo completes leadership training course   No gender more important than the other – Yul Edochie     Mary Njoku: quit age-shaming or else…     Many unsuccessful years behind every successful man, not…   tochukwujoyce asked: “where is the lie ….?” i__train_people_into_tech said: “No truer words !!!!” godriic1 wrote: “When you have money almost everything becomes possible for you.” mr.sunqie stated: “Lack of money go stress you.. Stress go lead to depression..” bimpsbiade said: “Honestly it is, the only stress i have now is Money Stress….” iam_benkid wrote: “With money life will be so much easier than harder.” yinye_diobi stated: “Very accurate.” joycatch_sam said: “No lie detected.” magicalglowskincare wrote: “Absolute truth.”